<% layout("../layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/hosting-guide.css">

<div class="info-page">
    <div class="info-container">

        <div class="page-header">
            <i class="bi bi-house-heart"></i>
            <h1>Hosting Guide</h1>
            <p>Everything you need to know to become a successful host on VibeStay.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-1-circle"></i> Create Your Listing</h2>
            <p>
                Start by adding your property details, high-quality photos,
                room information, amenities, pricing, and location.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Add clear and attractive photos.</li>
                <li>Write an accurate property description.</li>
                <li>Set competitive room prices.</li>
                <li>Mention all available amenities.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-2-circle"></i> Manage Booking Requests</h2>
            <p>
                Guests can send booking requests based on room availability.
                Review every request carefully before approving or rejecting it.
            </p>

            <div class="tip-box">
                <i class="bi bi-lightbulb"></i>
                <span>Respond quickly to improve guest satisfaction.</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-3-circle"></i> Keep Availability Updated</h2>
            <p>
                Ensure that room availability and pricing remain accurate.
                Incorrect availability may result in guest dissatisfaction.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-4-circle"></i> Provide Great Hospitality</h2>
            <p>
                Positive guest experiences lead to better reviews,
                more visibility, and increased bookings.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Maintain cleanliness.</li>
                <li>Offer prompt communication.</li>
                <li>Provide accurate property information.</li>
                <li>Be professional and respectful.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-5-circle"></i> Earn Trust Through Reviews</h2>
            <p>
                Guests may leave reviews after their stay. Consistently
                positive reviews help your property stand out.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> Hosting Best Practices</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Verify all property information before publishing.</li>
                <li>Keep prices transparent.</li>
                <li>Avoid last-minute cancellations.</li>
                <li>Maintain a safe environment for guests.</li>
                <li>Follow all local laws and regulations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>